div(class="type-demo")
    div(class="type-demo__name type-demo__h1") H1
    h1(class="type-demo__example heading1") This one is the sub-section or widget title
    div(class="type-demo__name type-demo__h2") H2
    h2(class="type-demo__example heading2") Next one is the item title inside widgets
    div(class="type-demo__name type-demo__h3") H3
    h3(class="type-demo__example heading3") This is a label or CTA text
    div(class="type-demo__name type-demo__body") Body
    div(class="type-demo__example") 
        div(class="type-demo__bodystyle") This is the body text which is used for most of the design, like paragraphs, lists, etc.
